Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:24.37,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Zase budeme meškať, ak si nepohneme!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.17,opt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, áno.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:29.85,opt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, čo Nemu povedala je pravda.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:32.03,opt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ako obvykle, sme...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.03,0:04:32.71,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:38.83,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoriko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:42.99,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo sa tak divne tváriš?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:45.73,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, uh to nič...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:47.67,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak poďme! Prídeme neskoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:51.75,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Si divný, Junichi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:52.81,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Súdiac podľa výrazu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:55.92,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabudol si si zase domáce úlohy, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:57.05,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Úlohy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.38,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Mali sme nejaké?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:01.44,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno mali sme.
