Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:07.03,opt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, chápem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:08.29,opt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Toto je sen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:12.39,opt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}V tomto sne som spolužiakom Yoriko-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:17.99,opt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Máme rovnakú domácu a sme v rovnakej triede.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:20.87,opt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A...{\i0}
