Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:30.95,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozri, Junichi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:39.09,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to tak záhadné, nie?
