Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:54.13,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:55.67,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:01.27,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Deje sa niečo?
