Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:05.03,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoriko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.41,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, to nič.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:10.92,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to tak?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:14.04,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak sa prosím, rýchlo obleč.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:16.22,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Pripravila som pre teba raňajky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:23.64,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Vydesila ma.
