Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:39.06,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, mám ho rád.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:40.61,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Mám ho rád, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:44.75,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurá! Poďme jesť!
